ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectOrder Approving the Boundary Change of the Chambre de commerce et d’industrie de Thetford Mines inc.
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D’INDUSTRIE DE THETFORD MINES INC., in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from Black Lake, Rivière Blanche, Thetford-Mines, Thetford Sud, Robertsonville, Pontbriand, St-Daniel, Irlande Sud, Irlande Nord, St-Méthode and St-Jean de Bréboeuf to Thetford Mines, Irlande, Saint-Jean-de-Brébeuf, Adstock, Saint-Adrien-d’Irlande, East-Broughton, Sacré-Coeur-de-Jésus , Sainte-Clotilde-de-Beauce, Saint-Jacques-de-Leeds, Saint-Pierre-de-Broughton, Kinnear’s Mills, Saint-Joseph-de-Coleraine, and Sainte-Praxède.
